text: The CIT Paraguay Open was a tournament for professional female tennis players played on outdoor clay courts. The event was classified as a $50,000 ITF Women's Circuit tournament and was first and only held in Asunción, Paraguay, in 2014. == Past finals == === Singles === {|class="wikitable" style="font- size:90%" |- !Year !width="200"|Champion !width="200"|Runner-up !width="175"|Score |- | 2014 || Bianca Botto || Florencia Molinero || 6–3, 6–2 |} === Doubles === {|class="wikitable" style="font-size:90%" |- !Year !width="200"|Champions !width="200"|Runners-up !width="175"|Score |- | 2014 || Sofía Luini Guadalupe Pérez Rojas || Anastasia Pivovarova Patricia Maria Țig || 6–3, 6–3 |} == External links == * Official website * ITF search Category:ITF Women's Circuit Category:Clay court tennis tournaments Category:Tennis tournaments in Paraguay Category:Recurring sporting events established in 2014 Category:Recurring sporting events disestablished in 2014 Category:Defunct sports competitions in Paraguay
